- Ratio: We staff to maintain a low, consistent ratio with two educators in the room for core parts of the day (arrival through early afternoon), and we adjust staffing for peak times (drop-off/pick-up, outdoor play) to keep supervision strong.

- Outdoor time: Outdoor play is built in daily (weather permitting). If weather is unsafe (e.g., severe conditions), we replace it with active indoor movement and gross-motor play.
